---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="personal-website 预览入口" currentPath="/preview/">
  <section class="preview-page section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">DESIGN PREVIEW</p>
      <h1>个人网站 v2 入口</h1>
      <p class="lead">这个页面只用于检查交付范围。真实站点入口仍然是首页。</p>

      <div class="preview-grid" aria-label="页面入口">
        <a href="/">
          <span>01</span>
          <strong>主页</strong>
          <p>身份定位、内容主线、最新文章和公众号关注。</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/">
          <span>02</span>
          <strong>文章列表</strong>
          <p>按时间倒序展示文章，突出扫描效率。</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/2026-06-07-65-lines-karpathy/">
          <span>03</span>
          <strong>文章详情</strong>
          <p>长文阅读、目录、代码块和文末关注入口。</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
